        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nThe way this is muddying up DefaultPfDao, I'm beginning to wonder if we should go back and make PfReferenceTimestampKey Embeddable again.  That may entail lifting duplicate code from the current superclass, which would probably trigger a complaint from sonar, but isolating that to one class, PfReferenceTimestampKey, seems preferable to me.",
